#: ../../effects_and_filters/titles.rst:109
msgid "Holding :kbd:`Shift + Alt` move selected items horizontally only."
msgstr ""
"Se tieni premuto :kbd:`Alt` sposti gli elementi selezionati solo "
"orizzontalmente."

#: ../../effects_and_filters/titles.rst:111
msgid ""
"Once done click :guilabel:`Create Title` (bottom right) or :guilabel:`Update "
"Title`."
